      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector's dream. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. Every feature and component functions exactly as it did the day it was manufactured. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in such impeccable, like-new condition.",
